metadata.name: Trick OR Treat 2022
metadata.description: 100 Winners when the collection mints out. 95 people will win 1 Eth, and 5 people will win 5 Eth!!! Reveal will happen 1 week after minting out, and if your pumpkin shows TREAT, then you win 1 Eth. If your pumpkin shows MEGA TREAT, then you win 5 Eth!
